1977;;The Love Letters from Teralba Road;;Australian;;Stephen Wallace;;Kris McQuade, Bryan Brown, Gia Carides;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Love_Letters_from_Teralba_Road;;Len (Bryan Brown) and his wife Barbara (Kris McQuade) have separated after he beat her in a drunken rage. He tries to get her back with a series of letters.